README
---------------------------------------------------------------------

This project consists of two parts, the letterbox module and the
mobile client.


    LETTERBOX

Build requirements:
    python, gcc-avr, binutils-avr, avr-libc, avrdude

Build using:
    ./make.py


    MOBILE CLIENT

Build requirements:
   Java JDK, Java Wireless Toolkit, ant, ant-optional

Build using:
    cd mobile/mobile-letterbox-client
    ant
 
Note: You might have to specify the property 'platform.home' in 
mobile/mobile-letterbox-client/nbproject/private/private.properties
If this file does not exist, create it. The property 'platform.home'
should point to the installation directory of the Wireless Toolkit.
    
